{"tid":2421040,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"財委會討論「為接種2019冠狀病毒病疫苗後出現的異常事件設立的保障基金」","createTime":"2021-02-24T08:50:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T08:52:05.000Z","uid":323538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8f005998e70cbf2e72a423487fc40d7487ca2cfb","tid":2421040,"uid":323538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T08:50:43.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">屌！</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n財務委員會討論文件<br />\n2021年2月26日<br />\n<br />\n政府擬為接種2019冠狀病毒病疫苗(下稱「新冠疫苗」)後出現的異常事件設立保障基金(下稱「保障基金」)。保障基金涵蓋雙邊採購協議下向疫苗製造商提供的保障，以及為在接種新冠疫苗後出現<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"blue\">非預期的嚴重異常事件</span></strong></span>並能提供有關證明的人士提供財政援助。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A3n8qc7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA3n8qc7.png&h=ee81374c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr20-21/chinese/fc/fc/papers/f20-94c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr20-21%2Fchinese%2Ffc%2Ffc%2Fpapers%2Ff20-94c.pdf&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8ADrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=dc43b22f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr20-21/chinese/fc/fc/papers/f20-94c.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"1497c82c820d0599c5a3b9a5f081e9adc52a1275","tid":2421040,"uid":323538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T08:52:05.000Z","msg":"推"}]}